<p>If Pervez Musharraf had just declared himself King of Pakistan years back no one would have minded (except me; personally I hate kings ("mostly rapscallions")). Do we ever ask the king of Saudi Arabia or queen of England to step down in favor of a democratically elected head of state?</p>

